observations.recommendation:
The Municipal Treasurer and Municipal Accountant update its Real Property Tax Account Register (RPTAR)/Taxpayer’s index card based on the assessment roll and provide a summary list to the Accounting Unit;

The Municipal Treasurer and Municipal Accountant set up the real property and special education tax receivables at the beginning of each year based on the certified list amount due and collectible for the year under the NGAS Manual for LGUs;

Adhere to the accounting and procedural rules and regulations in the monitoring and recording its real property accounts; and

Reconcile the noted abnormal balances and make the necessary adjustments on its RPT and SET balances as warranted.

We reiterated our recommendation and:
The Municipal Treasurer agreed to update its RPTAR/Taxpayer’s index card based on the assessment roll and provide a certified list to the Accounting Unit;
The Municipal Accountant agreed to set up the real property and special education tax receivables at the beginning of each year based on the certified list amount due and collectible for the year under the MNGAS for LGUs;
The Municipal Accountant agreed to adhere to the accounting and procedural rules and regulations in the monitoring and recording its real property accounts; and
The Municipal Accountant agreed to verify the balances of RPT/SET Receivables and make the necessary adjustments on its RPT and SET balances, as warranted.

The Municipal Engineer agreed to submit the following for evaluation by the Audit Team:
SWA as of March 23, 2023, prepared by the Contractor and  reviewed and certified by the Municipal Engineer;
Inspection Report as of March 23, 2023;
Geotagged pictures or pictures with verifiable dates when taken to support the work accomplished as of March 23,  2023; 
Explanation on the 156-day delay in the accomplishment of the remaining 8.53% of the unperformed portion of work; and
Copy of the As Built-plans of the subject infrastructure project.

We recommended that the Municipal Treasurer and Municipal Accountant:
